 \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":4362,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/08\/07\/worship-jihad-ten-nights-ramadan\/","url_meta":{"origin":972,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Ramadan: The Prophet strives in last ten nights","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 7, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Aisha reported: When the last ten nights of Ramadan arrived, the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, would tighten his belt, spend the night in worship, and awaken his family. Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 2024, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 1174 Grade: Muttafaqun Alayhi\u00a0(authenticity agreed upon) according to Al-Bukhari and Muslim \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064e\u0627\u0626\u0650\u0634\u064e\u0629\u064e\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":27531,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/04\/11\/prophet-connects-shaban-ramadan\/","url_meta":{"origin":972,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Sha\u2019ban: The Prophet fasts in Sha\u2019ban before Ramadan","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 11, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Aisha reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, would fast until we said he will never break his fast, and he would not fast until we said he would never fast. I did not see the Prophet complete an entire month of fasting except for Ramadan,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d